comments:
That part which until 1894 formed part of the parish of 
    Spotland. See also Table 2, note (d).
Abolished 1894 and added to the parish of Littleborough.

Abolished 1894 and divided between the parishes of Milnrow, Littleborough, 
    Rochdale and Wardle.

Abolished 1894 and divided between the parishes of Rochdale, Castleton 
    by Rochdale, Heywood and Milnrow.

Created 5.11.1896 by renaming the parish of Castleton by Rochdale. 
    Abolished 9.11.1900 and divided between the parishes of Rochdale and Bury. See 
    also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1894 from the parts of the parishes of Castleton, Thornham and Hopwood in Castleton by Rochdle Urban District. Renamed 5.11.1896 to become 
    the parish of Castleton Lancashire. See also Table 2, notes (a), (b) and (d).

That part which until 1894 formed part of the parish of Castleton by Rochdale. 
    See also Table 2, note (a).

That part which until 9.11.1900 formed part of the parish of 
    Castleton Lancashire. See also Table 2, note (e).

That part which until 1.4.1933 formed part of the parish of Norden. 
    See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1894 from the parts of the parishes of Blatchinworth & 
    Calderbrook, Butterworth and Wuerdle & Wardle, in Littleborough Urban District. 
    See also Table 2, note (h).

Created 1894 from the parts of the parishes of Butterworth and 
    Castleton in Milnrow Urban District. See also Table 2, note (h).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Spotland in Norden 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.10.1933 and divided between the parishes of Rochdale 
    and Heywood. See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1894 from the parishes of Castleton, Wardleworth, Sporland, 
    Wuerdle & Wardle and Butterworth. Abolished 1.4.1974 to become an unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1894 and divided between the parishes of Rochdale, Whitworth, 
    Bacup and Norden. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1894 from the parts of the parishes of Wuerdle & Wardle 
    and Butterworth in Wuerdle & Wardle Urban District. See also Table 2, note (h).
Abolished 1894 and added to the parish of Rochdale.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Spotland in Whitworth 
    Urban District. See also Table 2, note (h).
Abolished 1894 and divided between the parishes of Rochdale, Wardle and Littleborough.
